gions where {$<$}inline-formula xmlns:ifp="http://www.ifactory.com/press"{$><$}img src="jcli-d-17-0121.1-inf4.gif"{$><$}/img{$><$}/inline-formula{$>$} is particularly sensitive to the precipitation corrections (including the central United States, the Sahel, and parts of South Asia), the changes in the {$<$}inline-formula xmlns:ifp="http://www.ifactory.com/press"{$><$}img src="jcli-d-17-0121.1-inf5.gif"{$><$}/img{$><$}/inline-formula{$>$} {$<$}inline-formula xmlns:ifp="http://www.ifactory.com/press"{$><$}img src="jcli-d-17-0121.1-inf6.gif"{$><$}/img{$><$}/inline-formula{$>$} are relatively large, suggesting that the observed precipitation influenced the {$<$}inline-formula xmlns:ifp="http://www.ifactory.com/press"{$><$}img src="jcli-d-17-0121.1-inf7.gif"{$><$}/img{$><$}/inline-formula{$>$} performance.{$<$}/p{$><$}/section{$>$}},
